1. *Shvatam* da je to teško za razumeti. (I understand that it is hard to comprehend.)
2. Možda to nisam dovoljno dobro *shvatila*. (Maybe I didn't understand it well enough.)
3. Ponuđeni plan nisam *shvatila*. (I didn't understand the proposed plan.)
4. *Shvatam* da ne mogu da razumem sve. (I understand that I cannot understand everything.) 
5. Javila mi se prilika koju nisam *shvatila*. (An opportunity came up to me that I didn't understand.)
6. *Shvataš* li ono što ti govorim? (Do you understand what I'm telling you?) 
7. Ono što ti govorim, *shvataš*? (Do you understand what I'm telling you?)